Subject: sched/fair: Prevent dead task groups from regaining cfs_rq's
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b027789e5e50494c2325cc70c8642e7fd6059479
